name: Slack -> Keboola (BigQuery, Snowflake)
description:
This template connects to Slack, retrieves all messages and attachments from a chosen channel, and loads them into Snowflake or BigQuery via Keboola. Once in Keboola, the data can be processed, transformed, or sent to other destinations for further analysis.

Need help or have ideas? Contact us at support@keboola.com.
